reviewText: I just got this DVD this week and let me tell you, it really works your abs and it is not as easy as it looks. If you arecca beginner it will take time to get use to the exercises.  I would not attempt to do the advance ab crunches until I master the beginner's level.
This is a tough work  out. I had to stop and take a  break and start  again.  I would definitely recommend it.
